@HomeYarp.WebServer_HostAddress = http://localhost:5268

### List applications
GET {{HomeYarp.WebServer_HostAddress}}/api/applications
Accept: application/json

### Create an application (proxies echo.localhost -> postman-echo.com)
POST {{HomeYarp.WebServer_HostAddress}}/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "echo",
  "displayName": "Echo Test",
  "description": "Forwards echo.localhost to postman-echo.com",
  "enabled": true,
  "routes": [
    {
      "hosts": ["echo.localhost"],
      "path": "/{**catch-all}"
    }
  ],
  "cluster": {
    "destinations": [
      { "name": "primary", "address": "https://postman-echo.com" }
    ]
  }
}

### Proxy through YARP using the configured host header
GET {{HomeYarp.WebServer_HostAddress}}/get
Host: echo.localhost
